\item What percentage of your $p$-values are below 0.05?  What percentage would you expect by chance?
\item  Being less-than-scrupulous, you assert that you have found significant results--lots of them!  Why should your customers be wary of the claim that mailings have an impact?  
\item Explain why this process is termed ``data-fishing,'' and why it is frowned upon.
\end{itemize}
